# .deploy-allowlist
# Canonical, machine-readable list of files that may legitimately exist in
# Equipa-prod but NOT in upstream source. Read by scripts/deploy-equipa-prod.sh.
#
# Format: one relative path per line. Lines starting with '#' and blank lines
# are ignored. No globs — exact relative paths only, so the allowlist cannot
# accidentally widen.
#
# Keep this file in sync with:
#   - PROD_ONLY_FILES array in scripts/deploy-equipa-prod.sh
#   - section list in docs/PROD_ONLY.md.example
#   - EXPECTED_PROD_ONLY_FILES fixture in tests/test_deploy_script.py
dispatch_config.json
forge_config.json
mcp_config.json
theforge.db
.env
